dcterms:description: A large-scale fashion landmark dataset consisting of 30K images with comprehensive fashion landmark annotations, collected from fashion blogs, forums, and consumer-to-shop retrieval benchmarks. It reflects real-world variations and challenges in fashion image analysis.
dcterms:title: Unconstrained Landmark Database (ULD)

dcterms:description: A dataset for fashion landmark detection in the wild, focusing on images taken in various uncontrolled environments, which helps in understanding and detecting fashion landmarks under real-world conditions.
dcterms:title: Fashion Landmark Detection dataset (FLD)
